&lt;li&gt;Maintain professional and respectful behavior when in contact with customers, management, and teammates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present a polished personal appearance, adhering to company grooming standards outlined in the Employee Handbook.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adhere to all company policies and procedures outlined in handbooks, manuals, and other company documents.&lt;/li&gt;
